38 (2) Any person utilizing a wireless telecommunications device to display his or her
39 license in electronic format in order to comply with subsection (a) of this Code section
40 shall not be considered to have consented to a search of such device by a law enforcement
41 officer. No person shall be compelled to release his or her wireless telecommunications
42 device to a law enforcement officer pursuant to this Code section.
